## Development workflow

This project uses the [flow plugin](https://github.com/by-dev-tools/flow) for its 11-step managed-autonomy loop:

```
Clarify → Plan (gate) → Execute → Preflight → Commit → /simplify → /flow:staff-review → Present → Iterate → /flow:ship → User merges (gate)
```

See `CLAUDE.md` for the project's quality bar + doc index. Run `/flow:workflow-help` in a Claude Code session for the in-skill cheat sheet + your project's resolved `flow.config.json` slots.

